%F A011971 Double-exponential generating function: Sum_{n, k} a(n-k, k) x^n y^k / n! k! = exp(e^{x+y}-1+x). - _Don Knuth_, Sep 21 2002 [U coordinates, reversed]
%F A011971 a(n,k) = Sum_{i=0..k} binomial(k,i)*Bell(n-k+i). - _Vladeta Jovovic_, Oct 15 2006
